">已棄用</label>\n          \n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1dultl37tpkbd5rkiav33u8ax\">從 v6 開始</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"path\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">path</span>: string[]</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">只讀</span>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"49hnvk21xojxvnuwgsxbuct9t\">回傳一個陣列，該陣列表示從頂級表單到此控制元件的路徑。每個索引是該級別上控制元件的字串名稱。</p>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"control\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">control</span>: <a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">只讀</span>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c3fjogj5uiqmxoeg0efnen19e\">繫結到此指令的 <code><a href=\"api/forms/FormControl\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControl</a></code>。</p>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"inherited-members-list\">\n  <h3 id=\"繼承自-ngcontrol\">繼承自 <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/NgControl\">NgControl</a></code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormControlDirective#繼承自-ngcontrol\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/NgControl#name\"><span class=\"member-name\">name</span>: string | number | null</a></code>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n      <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/NgControl#valueAccessor\"><span class=\"member-name\">valueAccessor</span>: ControlValueAccessor | null</a></code>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"inherited-members-